&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clinical Coding Assistant &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a vacancy within the Clinical Coding Department for a Coding Assistant. This is a customer focused role that requires an enthusiastic and self-motivated person who can remain calm in a busy environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be responsible for retrieving and providing casenotes for all discharged patients. The Trust has very strict deadlines in which all episodes must be coded. In order to ensure all the casenotes are available on time the successful candidate will be able to demonstrate a high level of efficiency and determination.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, friendly and hard working individual, you should have excellent communication skills, with a ‘can do’ attitude and good IT skills.&lt;/p&gt;
